        {
            "title": "澳門2月賭收197.4億 按年增長6.8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"澳門2月賭收197.4億 按年增長6.8%\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ee1cb1fe4393241b2a5f41ddc448301f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030117300313292.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">澳門2月賭收197.4億 按年增長6.8%</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>據澳門博彩監察協調局數據顯示，澳門2月幸運博彩毛收入197.4億澳門元，按年增長6.8%，超過市場預期。今年首兩月賭收合計380億澳門元，按年增長0.5%\n\n</p>\n<p>值得留意是，澳門賭收低於2019年疫情前的水平。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2055697/即時-財經-澳門2月賭收197-4億-按年增長6-8",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-01 17:46:07",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "25歲販毒女還押前體內藏毒 大欖女懲教所人員及時發現",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"25歲販毒女還押前體內藏毒 大欖女懲教所人員及時發現\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bd99e87eb08e12909040255847811a6f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030117282316754.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">25歲販毒女還押前體內藏毒 大欖女懲教所人員及時發現</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一名25歲女子2月18日因販運危險藥物罪，被還押於大欖女懲教所。懲教人員透過X光身體掃描器檢查，懷疑她收押前曾吞下毒品，於是將她隔離並密切監察。該名還押女囚繼上星期五（2月21日）排出一包用膠紙包裝的懷疑毒品後，於今日上午11時02分再排出3包合共約重38克用膠紙包裝的懷疑毒品。\n\n</p>\n<p>懲教署稱，已將案件轉介警方跟進，又強調署方一直竭力堵截毒品及未獲授權物品流入懲教院所，以確保懲教院所的良好秩序及維持「零毒品」的羈押環境。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
