        {
            "title": "啟德開幕禮｜鄧炳強提早到場 視察場外保安及人流管制部署",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"啟德開幕禮｜鄧炳強提早到場 視察場外保安及人流管制部署\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/185577b27dacd08628dc7e8cf4463cb8/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030116342421870.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">啟德開幕禮｜鄧炳強提早到場 視察場外保安及人流管制部署</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>啟德體育園今天（3月1日）正式開幕，啟德主場館將於傍晚6時30分舉行盛大開幕禮，屆時將逾3萬名觀眾出席。為確保開幕禮順利進行，保安局局長鄧炳強、副局長卓孝業及常任秘書長李百全，提到於下午4時到場，視察場外保安及人流管制部署。期間，一行人與在場的工作人員、民安隊、醫療輔助隊等交談，了解部署細節，並為他們打氣。\n\n</p>\n<p>為配合啟德體育園開幕，啟德及宋皇臺站今晚（3月1日）將實施客流管理措施，個別出入口會作單向進出安排。活動散場時，乘客或需於站外等候分批進入車站，港鐵會按需要加密列車班次。當局呼籲市民保持忍讓，耐心等候並為行程預留充裕時間。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關報道：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/society/3433557\">啟德開幕禮｜觀眾提早零售館用膳準備入場 讚現場配套完善</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111731/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄧炳強卓孝業一行人視察人流管制措施。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/27784d3f9f6d3294a9413704e7fba63a/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_161636274_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧炳強卓孝業一行人視察人流管制措施。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111729/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄧炳強與醫療輔助隊人員交談。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6dd95436808372e473a6e9c018ebe929/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_161639439.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧炳強與醫療輔助隊人員交談。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111730/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄧炳強與民安隊人員交談。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f10f5fd0b76727588cbcfeda7b7affba/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_161637315_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧炳強與民安隊人員交談。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111735/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"鄧炳強一行人提早體育園主場館外視察。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7b6ac22df2787882564d4a5da03519ed/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_161626864_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        鄧炳強一行人提早體育園主場館外視察。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111734/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/404418bfda95806ccdb16f6524376df0/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_161632778.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111733/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/479e33fc7ea18a14cfe27499a348b5da/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_161627996_0.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
